.SS m060-doctor
.TP
\f[B]sovereign-osctl m060-doctor [arguments]\f[R]
MS022 SSE subscriber-quota chain triage \[em] probes the 4 consumer-
side surfaces (proxy daemon, master-dashboard banner, systemd unit)
against the selfdef-side producer state (selfdef commit 77b4499 6
gauges).
Read-only (R10212 + R10115).
Stdlib-only Python; no deps.
Exit codes: 0=GREEN / 1=YELLOW / 2=RED.
Flags: \[en]strict requires state=ok everywhere; \[en]json for
machine-readable triage.
See scripts/diagnostics/ms022-doctor.py \[en]help for the full flag
surface.
.PP
